###Block: Creature Traits
Aversion to Fire	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:If the creature takes Fire damage, it has Disadvantage on attack rolls and ability checks until the end of its next turn.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Aversion to Fire																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Battle Ready	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature has Advantage on Initiative rolls.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Battle Ready																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Beast Whisperer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature can communicate with Beasts as if they shared a common language.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Beast Whisperer																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Death Jinx	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When the creature dies, one random creature within 10 feet of the dead creature is targeted by a Bane spell (save DC 13), which lasts for its full duration.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Death Jinx																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Dimensional Disruption	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Disruptive energy extends from the creature in a 30-foot Emanation. Other creatures can't teleport to or from a space in that area. Any attempt to do so is wasted.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Dimensional Disruption																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Disciple of the Nine Hells	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When the creature dies, its body disgorges a Hostile Imp in the same space.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Disciple of the Nine Hells																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Disintegration	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When the creature dies, its body and nonmagical possessions turn to dust. Any magic items it possessed are left behind in its space.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Disintegration																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Emissary of Juiblex	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When the creature dies, its body disgorges a Hostile Ochre Jelly in the same space.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Emissary of Juiblex																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Fey Ancestry	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature has Advantage on saving throws it makes to avoid or end the Charmed condition, and magic can’t put it to sleep.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Fey Ancestry																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Forbiddance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature can't enter a residence without an invitation from one of its occupants.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Forbiddance																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Gloom Shroud	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:imperceptible energy channeled from the Shadowfell extends from the creature in a 20-foot Emanation. Other creatures in that area have Disadvantage on Charisma checks and Charisma saving throws.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Gloom Shrouds																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Light	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature sheds Bright Light in a 10-foot radius and Dim Light for an additional 10 feet. As a Bonus Action, the creature can suppress this light or cause it to return. The light winks out if the creature dies.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Light																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Mimicry	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature can mimic Beast sounds and Humanoid voices. A creature that hears the sounds can tell they are imitations with a successful DC 14 Wisdom (Insight) check.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Mimicry																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Poison Tolerant	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature has Advantage on saving throws it makes to avoid or end the Poisoned condition.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Poison Tolerant																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Resonant Connection	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature has a supernatural connection to another creature or an object and knows the most direct route to it, provided the two are within 1 mile of each other.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Resonant Connection																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Siege Monster	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature deals double damage to objects and structures.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Siege Monster																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Slaad Host	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:When the creature dies, a Hostile Slaad Tadpole bursts from its innards in the same space.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Slaad Host																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Steadfast	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature has Immunity to the Frightened condition while it can see an ally within 30 feet of itself.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Steadfast																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Telepathic Bond	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature is linked psychically to another creature. While both are on the same plane of existence, they can communicate telepathically with each other.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Telepathic Bond																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Telepathic Shroud	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature is immune to any effect that would sense its emotions or read its thoughts, as, well as to spells from the school of Divination. As a Bonus Action, the creature can suppress this trait or reactivate it.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Telepathic Shroud																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Ventriloquism	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Whenever the creature speaks, it can choose a point within 30 feet of itself; its voice emanates from that point.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Ventriloquism																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Warrior's Wrath	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The creature has Advantage on melee attack rolls against any Bloodied creature,.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Warrior's Wrath																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Wild Talent	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Creature Trait.SpecialQuality	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Choose one cantrip; the creature can cast that cantrip without spell components, using Intellgence, Wisdom, or Charisma as the spelicasting ability.	KEY:Creature Trait ~ Wild Talent																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG


