###Block: Blessings
Blessing of Health	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Blessing.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your Constitution score increases by 2, up to a maximum of 22.	KEY:Blessing ~ Blessing of Health						BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Blessing Score Increase +1|2																					SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Blessing of Magic Resistance	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Blessing.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You have Advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.	KEY:Blessing ~ Blessing of Magic Resistance																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Blessing of Protection	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Blessing.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:You gain a +1 bonus to AC and saving throws.	KEY:Blessing ~ Blessing of Protection						BONUS:COMBAT|AC|1	BONUS:SAVE|ALL|1																				SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Blessing of Understanding	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Blessing.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Your Wisdom score increases by 2, up to a maximum of 22.	KEY:Blessing ~ Blessing of Understanding						BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Blessing Score Increase +1|2																					SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Blessing of Valhalla	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Blessing.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:This Blessing grants you the power to summon spirit warriors, as if you are blowing a silver Horn of Valhalla. Once you use this Blessing, you can't use it again until 7 days have passed.	KEY:Blessing ~ Blessing of Valhalla																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Blessing of Weapon Enhancement	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Blessing.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:One nonmagical weapon in your possession becomes a +1 Weapon while you wield it.	KEY:Blessing ~ Blessing of Weapon Enhancement																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG
Blessing of Wound Closure	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Racial Traits.Blessing.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:This Blessing grants you the benefits of a Periapt of Wound Closure.	KEY:Blessing ~ Blessing of Wound Closure																											SOURCEPAGE:DMG

+1 Increase Constitution	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Blessing Increase	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Increase your Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 22.	KEY:BL Increase ~ Con	!PRESTAT:1,CON=22	BONUS:STAT|CON|1		SOURCEPAGE:PHB
+1 Increase Wisdom	CATEGORY:Internal	TYPE:Blessing Increase	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Increase your wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 22.	KEY:BL Increase ~ Wis	!PRESTAT:1,WIS=22	BONUS:STAT|WIS|1		SOURCEPAGE:PHB

